                <head>No. 184.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Welsh</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Evarts</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1878-08-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 17, 1878</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Evarts</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary, Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Having applied for Condon’s pardon, am informed that it [will be] granted,
                    provided Queen approves. I hope to hear definitely 20th.</p>
                <p>My information being unofficial, no mention should be made until you are further
                    advised.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WELSH,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Minister</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
